es better than that."],[9021,9100,"It's not so bad."],[9192,9355,"I mean, they're like 20 cents each."],[9355,9451,"You can survive on a dollar a day."],[9451,9597,"Hey, have you ever tried it?"],[9597,9743,"I cannot say that I've had the pleasure."],[9743,9788,"No."],[9918,9964,"Well."],[10139,10256,"If you're a good boy,"],[10347,10489,"maybe I'll make you some one day."],[11407,11582,"I already told you, Karissa,"],[11636,11761,"I'm not a good boy."],[12716,12800,"Watch out!"]],"24":[[12,95,"Watch out!"],[392,517,"Karissa, hey, are you okay?"],[600,746,"Yeah, yeah, I'm fine."],[746,921,"That guy almost killed me!"],[938,1063,"Who drives like that?"],[2177,2256,"Hey."],[2281,2369,"No, no, no."],[2419,2527,"No, no, no, no,"],[2527,2640,"please, please, please..."],[2869,2994,"No!"],[3244,3282,"No."],[3349,3566,"I won't let this happen again."],[3699,3812,"Look, it's just business."],[3895,3933,"What?"],[3978,4020,"Okay?"],[4020,4154,"I've made a lot of enemies out there."],[4220,4325,"And they're gonna wanna hurt you"],[4341,4479,"just for being with me, I..."],[4479,4600,"I wasn't lying about that."]],"25":[[237,387,"But I would die,"],[421,592,"before I let anybody hurt you."],[721,804,"Okay?"],[1163,1230,"Let's go."],[1805,1868,"Whoa."],[1939,2106,"We're going to Carmine's?"],[2185,2394,"It's impossible to get a reservation now."],[2506,2619,"We don't need a reservation."],[3282,3457,"I'm sorry, we're fully booked tonight."],[3561,3799,"Why don't you do me a favor, sweetheart?"],[3812,3941,"Why don't you run in the back,"],[3987,4058,"tell the head chef that"],[4058,4154,"Vitale..."],[4175,4275,"sends his regards."],[4471,4567,"I was mistaken."],[4567,4671,"I think we might have a table"],[4671,4750,"for you after all."],[4954,5025,"Huh."],[5046,5209,"Since when does a gun for hire get this"],[5209,5288,"kind of treatment?"],[5309,5430,"In all the movies I've seen"],[5430,5568,"they've been at the bottom of the"],[5568,5643,"pecking order."],[6264,6410,"What can