s on you."],[2068,2143,"Ok."],[2256,2385,"I'll tell you about my family,"],[2431,2502,"but you first..."],[2790,2940,"You never talked about your ex-wife."],[3244,3365,"She's not my ex-wife."],[3486,3536,"She's a-"],[3536,3603,"Wait."],[3649,3687,"What?"],[3699,3828,"You're still married, Naz?"],[3878,4079,"She died protecting me from a madman."],[4220,4346,"She was pregnant with our child."],[4458,4567,"I'm so sorry."],[4688,4850,"Wherever he is, I'm going to find him."],[4938,5055,"I'm going to make sure he knows"],[5055,5209,"what it feels like to lose a wife..."],[5359,5434,"and a child."],[5701,5776,"Enough about me."],[5901,5993,"Alright, why don't you tell me"],[5993,6085,"about your family?"],[6272,6398,"It's just me and my mom."],[6498,6673,"And she holds on a little tight."],[6690,6856,"It's just because I'm all she has."],[6936,7061,"There's no father around?"],[7194,7349,"No, he left before I was born."],[7419,7553,"Mom doesn't like to talk about it,"],[7574,7761,"so I can't really know the details."],[7782,7945,"Well, in my eyes, he's a coward"],[7991,8158,"for leaving behind his wife and kid."],[8445,8500,"You know what?"],[8708,8812,"I'll take your offer,"],[8867,8938,"Karissa."],[9054,9125,"I'll protect you."],[9221,9334,"I'll do everything"],[9371,9559,"in my power to keep her safe."],[9622,9701,"Even if it means"],[9701,9855,"she becomes my greatest weakness."],[9880,9926,"Really?"],[10126,10243,"Okay, well then tell me your terms."],[10243,10331,"Anything you want."],[10447,10573,"All you have to do..."],[10731,10844,"is come home with me."]],"30":[[625,763,"Remember last time I was here,"],[763,842,"you kicked me out."],[980,1042,"That was rough."],[1255,1409,"Oh, no one has ever looked at me"],[1409,1509,"the way Naz does."],[1522,1655,"It's kind of..."],[1730,1801,"scary."],[1868,2027,"But why do I like it so much?"],[2143,2406,"You don't have to be afraid anymore."],[4600,4696,"No one"],[4696,4879,"will ever touch you"],[4984,5046,"again."],[6