ved me."],[2748,2823,"I'm gonna go look for her"],[2823,2890,"in the bedroom."],[3065,3123,"Just hang out here"],[3123,3203,"for a little while rest."],[5426,5584,"My mom had a best friend."],[5584,5726,"Why don't I know anything about her?"],[6022,6210,"Is that my father?"],[6944,7023,"What's going on here?"]],"62":[[187,250,"Naz?"],[400,479,"Naz Vitale?"],[896,996,"Hey, calm down, calm down."],[996,1134,"It's okay, it's okay."],[1155,1222,"Just stay here."],[1222,1347,"I'm gonna explain everything to her,"],[1347,1397,"okay?"],[2844,2902,"He found us."],[2944,3036,"It's not safe here anymore."],[3036,3123,"We have to get out of here."],[3123,3190,"Karissa, run!"],[3190,3265,"Stop! Stop!"],[3265,3370,"I'm not going anywhere."],[3370,3440,"You saw it yourself."],[3474,3532,"We're together."],[3557,3703,"Mom, I love him."],[3841,3912,"You..."],[3987,4141,"You don't know what you're talking about."],[4166,4379,"He's the Mafia king and I have done"],[4379,4475,"everything in my power to"],[4475,4583,"keep you away from him!"],[4583,4725,"I know you think that people like him"],[4725,4775,"are dangerous."],[4775,4871,"I know, I get that,"],[4871,5005,"but Naz is different."],[5005,5071,"No, don't,"],[5071,5167,"you cannot be with him!"],[5167,5246,"I will not allow it!"],[5246,5367,"You don't get to make your own"],[5367,5430,"decisions for me!"],[5430,5563,"I'm staying with him!"],[5563,5643,"Like hell, you will."],[5684,5722,"Mom."],[5880,5993,"I knew you looked familiar."],[6197,6277,"You're Grace Reed."],[6577,6715,"You married John Bass!"],[6810,6873,"Which means"],[6873,7002,"you're John's daughter."]],"63":[[0,75,"Please."],[141,241,"Please, Naz."],[308,375,"Please let her go."],[375,554,"She's innocent in all of this."],[554,608,"Please."],[1155,1284,"Mom, what are you talking about?"],[1284,1372,"What is going on?"],[1372,1480,"Someone tell me what's going on,"],[1480,1539,"please."],[1539,1618,"Your father,"],[1868,2010,"your father John Bass,"],[2043,2310,"murdered my wife and my unborn child."],[2331,2502,"He took everything from me."],[2606,2660,"My..."],[2715,2769,"My father is..."],[2936,2986,"It was him?"],[3040,3144,"She died protecting me"],[3144,3224,"from a madman."],[3395,3495,"She was pregnant with her child."],[3557,3737,"Wherever he is, I'm gonna find him."],[3803,3916,"I'm gonna make sure he knows"],[3916,4054,"what it feels like to lose a wife,"],[4229,4283,"and a child."],[5438,5538,"I never imagined..."],[5568,5709,"The traitor that I tracked down"],[5709,5818,"for ten years,"],[5826,6026,"that his daughter was right by my side."],[6122,6202,"The entire time."],[6318,6398,"He has dreamed"],[6418,6577,"of killing the family of the man"],[6577,6627,"responsible,"],[6702,6898,"of killing my mother and..."],[6981,7065,"and me."],[7098,7144,"Oh God,"],[7186,7340,"it feels like he's killing me now."]],"64":[[487,588,"Wait, you said..."],[667,905,"You said that you would die for me."],[905,1067,"You said you would never hurt me."],[1088,1222,"You promised."],[2056,2177,"No, I lied."],[2298,2456,"I never even knew my father."],[2502,2581,"Please, I didn't know"],[2581,2644,"anything of this."],[2656,2752,"Okay, I promise."],[2752,2836,"I had no idea."],[2890,2961,"Let us go."],[2961,3003,"Let us go."],[3003,3132,"We have nothing to do with him."],[3269,3378,"I'm not gonna hurt you."],[3449,3532,"Even if fate,"],[3566,3691,"turns us against each other,"],[3691,3778,"I'm not gonna hurt you."],[3858,3903,"No!"],[4104,4166,"Red!"],[4304,4425,"Naz, red!"],[5221,5296,"Mom."]],"65":[[467,592,"How could he do that?"],[821,896,"How could..."],[896,1017,"How could he just"],[1109,1226,"murder an innocent"],[1226,1355,"pregnant woman?"],[1693,1839,"Maria was my closest friend."],[1939,1993,"And she was"],[2052,2235,"so happy when she found out she was"],[2235,2277,"pregnant."],[2335,2423,"But your father,"],[2619,2815,"he was swayed by a violent mafioso and"],[2815,3015,"decided that he would kill Naz"],[3128,3328,"and be